reviewtext: ** IMPORTANT NOTE: This product also fits theBrother PT-65 Labeler!!! (The description only lists the newer model label-makers.)I love my label-maker and can't imagine life without it. I label Rubbermaid totes, charging cables, A/V equipment, boxes, leftovers for the freezer, etc...and it always sticks to everything...and actually comes off cleanly as well. Just make sure whatever you're labeling is dust/dirt free and you'll be good to go.
